Rabbi Mukuru We Mu Israeri, Rabbi David Lau Anotambira MuProfita T.B. Joshua Mu Jerusarema

0:05:39.660,0:05:44.380
Ndiri kufara kuti muri kutipa nguva yenyu.

0:05:44.380,0:05:47.460
Munonzwa kuti uno musha wenyu.

0:05:47.460,0:06:05.660
Munoziva, muBhaibheri unogona kuwana mutsetse iwowu.

0:06:05.660,0:06:12.880
Uyu munhu uye munhu uyo akaberekwa panzvimbo ino.

0:06:12.880,0:06:21.160
Ana chipangamazano vedu vanotsanangura chikonzero nei Bhaibheri rinoti munhu uye munhu.

0:06:21.160,0:06:23.980
Sei kaviri?

0:06:23.980,0:06:36.960
Tsanangudzo yacho ndeye kuti, kutanga munhu akaberekerwa muno uye wechipiri kuti uyo akaberekwa muno mumweya.

0:06:36.960,0:06:47.420
Mumwe ane tarisiro ye kunzwa kuti arikumba pano akangofanana neuyo munhu akazvarwa pano.

0:06:47.420,0:06:54.860
