Ino inzvimbo yakanakisa chaizvo,

0:07:36.100,0:07:42.320
Ruropafadzo rwangu kukuonai pano uye kunzwa mashoko enyu.

0:07:42.320,0:07:46.000
Ndinoda kukuudzai umwe mutsetse.

0:07:46.000,0:07:56.420
Ino inzvimbo ya unogona kuwana marudzi ose evanhu.

0:07:56.420,0:08:07.280
Ndaive ku South Africa gore rakapera uye vakandibvunza pamusoro pe kusiyana kwe vanhu -

0:08:07.280,0:08:20.260
